<entry stylesheet="matteroverdrive:info/styles/guide.css">
    <page class="padded-page">
        <title size="2" class="matter-text small-title">Matter Scanner</title>
        <text class="matter-text text-block">The Matter Scanner is used to scann blocks for the matter network.</text>
		<text class="matter-text text-block">First you have to link it to an active Pattern Storage with enough space on the Pattern Drive.</text>
		<text class="matter-text text-block">Next you have to aim at the block you want to scan and hold the righte mouse button down.</text>
		<text class="matter-text text-block">Be warned that scanned blocks will be destroyed in the process.</text>
        <text class="matter-text text-block">To have a whole block scanned you have to scan it 10 times.</text>
    </page>
</entry>
